sql:
SELECT 
    birth_year, COUNT(*)
FROM
    (SELECT 
        customer_rk, YEAR(ANY_VALUE(birth_dt)) AS birth_year
    FROM
        cd_customers
    WHERE
        monthly_income_amt IN (50000 , 60000)
    GROUP BY customer_rk
    HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT monthly_income_amt) = 2) customer_salary
GROUP BY birth_year
ORDER BY birth_year
